{"tid":2203062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無牌載貨 巡警放生  全民檢測判上判 白牌車運樣本","createTime":"2020-09-15T05:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"20c4f5a4828938b22a2ee0290a4b08bfba3f8664","tid":2203062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/V5G65I77URCETLLW3PAFT6YI24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FV5G65I77URCETLLW3PAFT6YI24%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=10d1c114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FV5G65I77URCETLLW3PAFT6YI24%2F&h=4ac4a97a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/V5G65I77URCETLLW3PAFT6YI24/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n無牌載貨 巡警放生 <br />\n全民檢測判上判 白牌車運樣本<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】延長至昨日完結的全民檢測屢被揭發防疫安排粗疏，本報偵查發現，政府將全民檢測的物流運輸安排「判上判」，有中介臨急一個月內招募運送樣本車輛，客貨車嫌「錢少無肉食」拒絕接單，在人手嚴重不足情況下堅持組成「白牌七人車隊」，公然在警方眼下違法運送樣本至西環火眼實驗室，更預先向受聘司機下達封口令密冚。有立法會議員批評港府雙重標準，表面嚴厲打擊非法載客載貨，暗地為達成全民檢測而知法犯法。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：裝備不足 司機憂中招<br />\n<br />\n根據檢測流程，巿民在全港十八區的檢測中心完成採樣後，由車隊收集樣本運送至西環中山紀念公園火眼實驗室化驗，本報過去兩周跟蹤運送流程，估計至少有70輛車輛參與，當中只有一架為客貨車，其餘均為七人車，其中32架持中港車牌。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，車隊出發時段分為下午3時和晚上7時，每轉車會獲派至同區四至五。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2YpXtnyIp9ZWtHF1oDj6zgIEiKg=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQM6RSN5WZGRTN2Y6AO4MZ7DW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2YpXtnyIp9ZWtHF1oDj6zgIEiKg%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQM6RSN5WZGRTN2Y6AO4MZ7DW4.jpg&h=91a66d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■白牌七人車公然運送一箱箱檢測樣本至火眼實驗室，不少司機亦欠防護裝備，徒手搬貨。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n招聘出手低 貨van拒接<br />\n<br />\n車隊運作期間，警車長期駐紮中山紀念公園體育館內，不時有警員下車巡邏，然而。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名中港車司機L先生透露，有中介上月初出價約32,000元包月「連人帶車」招聘，希望能組成50至60人的車隊，每日下午3時至8時。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nL先生指疫情在港爆發已八個月，中港車司機因大部份關口被封而手停口停，由。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司機被封口 辯稱做義工<br />\n<br />\n記者曾於火眼實驗室外向至少七名司機查問，全部人均三緘其口，有司機更聲稱自己是「義工」。據。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7_xyc_GWze-l6lVh5mH_z06ZZoo=/1966x1091/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UCWSCY5RYBC7HADJ3MYWSK3PDQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7_xyc_GWze-l6lVh5mH_z06ZZoo%3D%2F1966x1091%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUCWSCY5RYBC7HADJ3MYWSK3PDQ.gif&h=8335bbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■入夜後實驗室外的白牌車隊形成車龍，警車 （箭嘴示）停泊在旁，未見警員上前了解。<br />\n<br />\n曾任立法會交通事務委員會副主席的譚文豪直斥政府「帶頭犯法」，過去幾年屢次打。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n負責推行全民檢測的公務員事務局表示，已委託物流及供應鏈多元技術研發中心處理保安和。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n67輛無出租汽車許可證<br />\n<br />\nLSCM發言人回應招標和批出合約時，清楚註明承辦商提供服務時須符合香港法例。根據承辦商提供的資料，負責這次服務的車輛皆具有出租。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jqipg8fkhNce_9TY4cdatiwRzgE=/982x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SE4PNTJOC5AVTFXHFJHXITFJPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjqipg8fkhNce_9TY4cdatiwRzgE%3D%2F982x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSE4PNTJOC5AVTFXHFJHXITFJPA.jpg&h=aac576af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■車隊中的中港車司機否認運送樣本。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署回覆本報指只有輕型貨車、中型貨車或重型貨車牌照能以出租或取酬方式載貨，署長亦。。。。。"},{"pid":"be7fc72733fa5c3f8ba43563357066ab8def4e78","tid":2203062,"uid":56806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:52:40.000Z","msg":"嚴正執法 只係一個政權自欺欺人嘅口號"},{"pid":"d4e966899f461c3b78701cf0269683e4cabb4b6e","tid":2203062,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6d82a3aeb3c276dcba8af1cdabdf7a0db72dc9","tid":2203062,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"支那嘅法治見識下"},{"pid":"a73a13ec43280a2f943b970129b8982605c0a4fc","tid":2203062,"uid":10850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a9d767a5ed9dc3b0a4dbdc2712deee16c56b120","tid":2203062,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"6f36a763c66b5467c61823ce5156a2252a88d419","tid":2203062,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"國家任務黑狗邊夠薑阻撓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfdba6b8f62496365579907b981b9479f0cda41","tid":2203062,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:56:52.000Z","msg":"蝈家任務, 全城放毒, 等你哋d港毒份子冇得走."}]}